      • Button

        public Button(float topLeftX,
      float bottomRightX,
      float topLeftY,
      float bottomRightY,
      ClickableMenuLayer menuSelect,
      Engine.Vector2 selector)
        Instantiates a new button. - Four floats used to construct a button
        Parameters:
        topLeftX - is the new topLeftX
        bottomRightX - is the new bottomRightX
        topLeftY - is the new topLeftY
        bottomRightY - is the new bottomRightY
        menuSelect - Move the menu to the selected button that is passed in as the selector
        selector - The button that the menu will highlight
